## 🐍 Python AI Service Rules
- FastAPI with Pydantic BaseModel for all I/O
- Use Google Gemini API — NEVER OpenAI
- All LLM calls in try/except
- Response format: { "success": bool, "data": ..., "message": str }
- One router file per AI feature in routers/
- LLM logic in services/llm.py
- Ask for GEMINI_API_KEY before writing any LLM code

